<h1>ekiben APT repository</h1>
<p>Install on Debian / Ubuntu (amd64 / arm64):</p>
<pre>curl -fsSLO https://kewingit.github.io/ekiben/ekiben-archive-keyring.deb
sudo apt install ./ekiben-archive-keyring.deb
sudo apt update &amp;&amp; sudo apt install ekiben</pre>
<p>Then future versions arrive via <code>sudo apt upgrade</code>.</p>
<p>Project: <a href="https://github.com/KewinGit/ekiben">github.com/KewinGit/ekiben</a></p>
